2. cs.MED (Medical Imaging) - The paper specifically focuses on the segmentation of liver metastases in ultrasound images of cancer patients, which falls under the domain of medical imaging. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses an interactive segmentation approach, which involves machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses an interactive segmentation approach, which involves artificial intelligence techniques. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves the retrieval of information from ultrasound images of cancer patients, which could fall under the domain of information retrieval.
